&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt; Builders who want to own outcomes, not tasks. Systems thinkers who balance precision with iteration while thinking about the big picture. Individuals who are energized by creating a category rather than competing in an existing one. You’ll join a team that has already proven what others said wasn’t feasible and is now scaling and upgrading our VLEO buses &amp;amp; payloads to serve mission sets across sensing, communications, and responsive operations.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;If you can feel the excitement running through your veins, apply to be one of the Bedo 100.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
